      <title>[Letter] 1818 Apr. 22, Cherokee Agency [to] John C. Calhoun / Return J. Meigs</title>
   </titleInfo>
   <abstract>This is a copy of a letter dated April 22, 1818 from Return J. Meigs of the Cherokee Agency to John C. Calhoun requesting the sum of $3472.00 for payment to John and Lewis Ross for expenditures in the Cherokee Agency. Following is a copy of a notice from John C. Calhoun approving the payment.</abstract>
